### Evaluate Trade
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/evaluate_trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSD",
  "direction": "BUY",
  "confidence": 0.67,
  "entry_price": 78000.0,
  "stop_loss": 77500.0,
  "take_profit": 79000.0,
  "lot_size": 0.05,
  "account_equity": 10000.0,
  "daily_loss": 0.0,
  "open_positions": 1,
  "volatility": 0.32,
  "spread": 12.5,
  "session": "LONDON"
}

